Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.80,0:02:00.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.81,0:02:10.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.11,0:02:12.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煞星魔龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.33,0:02:25.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终於要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.23,0:02:27.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我们的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.13,0:02:31.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么会那么大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.11,0:02:46.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑…可以粉碎灵魂的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.16,0:02:56.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉大人也真霸道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.96,0:02:59.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,限我们两天内就要出航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不可以再做海盗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么，为什么到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.58,0:03:19.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是很好玩，对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳舞的赏金我就不跟你拿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.01,0:03:49.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有这种女人，真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吧  波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讲过不用你来救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候为了要找船的资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.74,0:04:16.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留在村里的斯林和蕾里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.87,0:04:18.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从被海盗船攻击过的人口中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到一件非常惊人的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.41,0:04:27.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么，那是真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.95,0:04:30.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我亲眼看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那海盗船上有麻莫国的国微
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在船的正前方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.23,0:04:40.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻莫…莫非是亚喜拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的，我们要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.83,0:04:46.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在只有相信，等他们回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.94,0:04:49.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过几日就会有援军来到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.61,0:04:53.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且帕母他们也…所以 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.44,0:04:57.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有不祥的预感…  帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒂都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要小心，帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.11,0:05:27.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在要开始猎龙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家进入准备状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各队最好把距离拉开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.05,0:05:40.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那条不是小龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要让它知道我们的厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.89,0:05:46.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒂都，魔法就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.88,0:06:04.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，等机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.68,0:06:07.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，但是我军这么庞大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对付一只龙也太浪费了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会把它的心脏射穿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.72,0:06:18.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.73,0:06:19.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，蒂都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧，蒂都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.65,0:06:39.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，它来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在射还太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要它接近一点才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.77,0:07:09.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去引开它，蒂都你去施魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去掩护帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.02,0:07:16.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡修殿下，帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.82,0:07:20.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.17,0:07:35.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射击射击，让它知道我们的厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.65,0:07:44.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种状况...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.38,0:07:46.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要快一点，蒂都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.86,0:08:01.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们大地天空的风之王希鲁非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.67,0:08:13.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你使出龙卷风把那只龙困住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.49,0:08:30.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是风之精灵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.34,0:08:45.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，你这只妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.17,0:09:19.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然可以伤到我，你们这些人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.34,0:09:30.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我伤害你们的城市杀了不少人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.52,0:09:33.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会把你们全部杀光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.70,0:09:48.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事，但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.37,0:09:56.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，如果有人会法术 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.65,0:10:03.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,输了，我们彻底的输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.42,0:10:11.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉大人好像有侵入者来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有侵入者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.33,0:10:18.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，史梅蒂你也打不赢的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.54,0:10:24.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的年轻美丽比你高出许多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.01,0:10:29.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这种女人吗，真不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.55,0:10:31.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧，亚斯达鲁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.21,0:10:33.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用期待了，卡贝拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.92,0:10:37.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪个女人都比史蒂漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.59,0:10:44.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为史梅蒂的体格很美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用安慰我，基尔拉姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.43,0:10:50.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战士是不用装扮的，只要够强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会证明给你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.80,0:10:58.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣，才几个人就想闯入这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很厉害的人  还是很笨的傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.95,0:11:06.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是想杀我的笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.95,0:11:09.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会用我的手亲自去证实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.97,0:11:32.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么，快点走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么?  快点?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.59,0:11:53.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.26,0:11:56.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然不拿这些财宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.03,0:11:59.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是海盗船不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.07,0:12:06.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，这样我们的目的达成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.78,0:12:10.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻莫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.41,0:12:14.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻莫的军舰吗?  为什么·
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.58,0:12:18.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么讲，莫非亚喜拉在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.69,0:12:21.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.66,0:12:27.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你们这些小偷竟知道我的名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.43,0:12:31.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑色衣服…那就是亚喜拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.47,0:12:34.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇定一点，要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.31,0:12:42.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心，我也是个战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.94,0:12:45.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道他们的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.41,0:12:48.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去派几个人去对付他们，欧布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.15,0:12:52.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主宰着战争的神麻利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.22,0:12:58.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请现身，帮我们去打赢战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.99,0:13:05.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请给予我们知识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们战神麻利的力量吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.59,0:13:33.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在感觉到全身充满力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.47,0:13:40.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不错，小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是小女孩  我叫希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.81,0:13:50.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.21,0:13:56.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我，我可是训练过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.92,0:14:03.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万能的神  请使出破坏之焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.34,0:14:17.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的吧，这家伙是怪物吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.14,0:14:21.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.08,0:14:28.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不讲的话，我就让你死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑有反应，这个男人到底是·
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.30,0:14:52.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想拖下去了，看绝招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.22,0:15:03.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是没用的小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.15,0:15:07.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和谈，我们和谈，我讲对不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.69,0:15:19.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用至高的魔法将这里变成睡地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.31,0:15:30.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经没气了吗小女孩，真没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.66,0:15:44.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.39,0:15:45.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是义枝，小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.30,0:15:54.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你投降吧，你是赢不了我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.00,0:15:58.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.95,0:16:06.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.48,0:16:46.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒  破坏  毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.99,0:16:52.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.89,0:16:54.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙很强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的实力吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.94,0:17:04.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来刚才你一直在让我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.48,0:17:14.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣的家伙，他拥有战士精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但还是敌不过我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.30,0:17:33.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么，不要走，不准走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要打败这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.24,0:17:40.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了希利斯，我现在需要你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.35,0:17:54.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，不可以让它控制住你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.69,0:17:57.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.73,0:18:05.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分出胜负了，你乖乖投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.63,0:18:08.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还活着的人  我希望你放他们走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.71,0:18:16.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是他们的队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我计算错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.76,0:18:31.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以为带着大军就能打败煞星龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.06,0:18:33.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.16,0:18:38.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然杀死我军约七万士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母，今後该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.57,0:18:47.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始我只是个普通战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.74,0:18:53.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏丹，你带伤兵先回国去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.18,0:18:57.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是卡修殿下你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.85,0:19:03.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒龙一定要会魔法的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.86,0:19:05.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去莱登找斯林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.13,0:19:11.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在卡修．帕母．蒂都加快马鞭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.87,0:19:13.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去找斯林的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉他们已经往青龙岛出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.07,0:19:22.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森他们也一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯